<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #EF4444; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>📝 Issues with Your Registration</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</h2>
      
      <p>We've reviewed your registration for <strong><%= @registration.business_name %></strong> and found some issues that need to be addressed before we can proceed.</p>
      
      <p><strong>Reason for rejection:</strong></p>
      <div style="background: #FEE2E2; border: 1px solid #FECACA; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px;">
        <%= @reason %>
      </div>
      
      <p>Please log in to your account to make the necessary corrections and resubmit your registration.</p>
      
      <p>If you have questions about these issues, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>